Title: Work Order: The August Celestials I
Description:
<Yoon's familiar writing scrolls across the tattered paper.>

The trainees out at the Cradle of Chi-Ji are in need of striped melons. Apparently, they use them in their training exercises.

A representative will be by tomorrow to collect whatever striped melons you can spare.
ObjectivesText: Plant 8 Striped Melon Seeds on Sunsong Ranch.
